        <actionDate rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">2024-08-01</actionDate>
        <actionDescription>Enhanced calibration protocol issued. Firmware update v1.8.5 mandatory improving temperature compensation algorithm. Patients instructed to perform confirmatory finger-stick at glucose readings &lt;4.5 or &gt;13.9 mmol/L.</actionDescription>
